    <item>
      <title>中国地震后仍有12人失踪，137人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/dozen-still-missing-after-chinas-earthquake-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一晚间甘肃省西北部发生6.2级地震，周四仍有十几人失踪，网友质疑救援行动结束的速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/dozen-still-missing-after-chinas-earthquake-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 02:18:07 GMT</pubDate>
